{
  "schema_version": "0.1.1",
  "coverage": "REFERENCED_CLAIM_EVIDENCE_ONLY",
  "source_turns": [
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0001",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0001",
      "ordinal": 1,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "I want to build a small internal research intake tool called Atlas Workshop. It should take a folder of notes and produce a clean project brief without changing the source files.",
      "text_sha256": "1b4ed1fc7edddcd98969efc3051386c6bd32c63697386e2b43c6ff079d4285e8"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0003",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0003",
      "ordinal": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "The important part is that every claim in the brief must link back to the source note it came from.",
      "text_sha256": "c849a488959417416a54b7ba742efaed737f2fab722615bff4fae236a945b41d"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0005",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0005",
      "ordinal": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "Also, do not build cloud sync yet. I want the first version to run entirely on my computer.",
      "text_sha256": "8af2d4cb90f1df301255860bc116083e57e200015aa727eaa51d6fb76b6e195b"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0011",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0011",
      "ordinal": 11,
      "role": "assistant",
      "text": "Proposed architecture: Folder Scanner → Text Normalizer → Evidence Index → Brief Generator → Manifest and Checksums.",
      "text_sha256": "fc4a03217d67dbb7ec8d35c5edc5a86a4b7edc71c754cf2225a2444066ab0a92"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0017",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0017",
      "ordinal": 17,
      "role": "assistant",
      "text": "A better demonstration would produce separate artifacts: Project Brief, Source Index, Open Questions, Manifest, and checksums.",
      "text_sha256": "78318b1b22498ea76cdcaa4f5c06a034949c0d61a3d35a76458e1784b6256940"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0020",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0020",
      "ordinal": 20,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "I want stable IDs for every source file and recovered claim.",
      "text_sha256": "356fd6c41b89e4c1fb86e9e62c773c2fccdab48cbc81ca322cedb3fdcb4957fb"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0024",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0024",
      "ordinal": 24,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "AUTHORIZE_ATLAS_WORKSHOP_LOCAL_READ_ONLY_PROTOTYPE_WITH_TEXT_MARKDOWN_AND_JSON_INPUT_PROJECT_BRIEF_SOURCE_INDEX_OPEN_QUESTIONS_MANIFEST_AND_CHECKSUMS_NO_CLOUD_SYNC_NO_SOURCE_MUTATION",
      "text_sha256": "dc3118007e8a4003635f64508a647d8a3a439ddeb27bb6f7676fa9c8179e2327"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0049",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0049",
      "ordinal": 49,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "Could we also export the project brief as a polished PDF?",
      "text_sha256": "64826af20bdbb0dc08274e3eec9438b101da6b016fd5012f65e7759968875914"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0057",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0057",
      "ordinal": 57,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "You are right. Hold the PDF exporter. It is not part of the prototype acceptance gate.",
      "text_sha256": "439494905172d705f52b120553e76839ebd0cba3f68bae6da9ca2cbecd4c0043"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0062",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0062",
      "ordinal": 62,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "I ran it from D:\\Projects\\AtlasWorkshop and it failed because the path is hardcoded.",
      "text_sha256": "13138e76b24cdf509c063a1407f7c0f692410026c2db5e08ce33e21ff2550e30"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0066",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0066",
      "ordinal": 66,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "The terminal error says FileNotFoundError for C:\\Demo\\AtlasWorkshop\\fixture.",
      "text_sha256": "389359b8f0c3bd672974b5e4a0954b5b1c71054c5c8cc0d66212ecae87ce7f62"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0070",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0070",
      "ordinal": 70,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "AUTHORIZE_ATLAS_WORKSHOP_PATH_RESOLUTION_REPAIR_EXPLICIT_INPUT_ARGUMENT_PREFLIGHT_BEFORE_OUTPUT_CREATION_SOURCE_FIXTURE_READ_ONLY",
      "text_sha256": "d230e59e6849f7330c04af43a137ce55104a6f05e5ab17446a4c04804218e2d4"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0080",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0080",
      "ordinal": 80,
      "role": "assistant",
      "text": "The repaired prototype completed the fixture run.",
      "text_sha256": "a5235327fc454571b001359aefc063fd0bcb81b11c95791b0c1f7391c1f63519"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0082",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0082",
      "ordinal": 82,
      "role": "assistant",
      "text": "Six source records: four unique supported text sources, one exact duplicate, and one unsupported PNG. No source files changed.",
      "text_sha256": "de3b1eaf02c972f9f8588833f33b08fee138348aed829502c6dbde5c77f96f72"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0090",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0090",
      "ordinal": 90,
      "role": "assistant",
      "text": "The second run produced matching hashes for all golden outputs.",
      "text_sha256": "51ad8b5573869c3608d094deb2a6745912e2ee4c77f04932f6219d18b4db1528"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0096",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0096",
      "ordinal": 96,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "ACCEPT_ATLAS_WORKSHOP_FIXTURE_TESTED_LOCAL_BASELINE_WITH_DETERMINISTIC_OUTPUTS_SOURCE_TRACE_DUPLICATE_EVIDENCE_UNSUPPORTED_FILE_REPORTING_AND_ZERO_SOURCE_MUTATION",
      "text_sha256": "c8619d6c15433eeb06cea81e2ee0f32fa60093f7f19c298fda43bc0e9645c676"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0098",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0098",
      "ordinal": 98,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "Correct. Production deployment remains unauthorized until the operator interface and clean-checkout test are complete.",
      "text_sha256": "486cf2e718598d6e619e93b55210fe51c90f4873fcff35c12afec4212ddd906b"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0100",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0100",
      "ordinal": 100,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "What still needs to be built?",
      "text_sha256": "fe70372aae5c5c1cbf0c9d4252e63159dab7b4e122cce1db12f7263506a543bf"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0101",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0101",
      "ordinal": 101,
      "role": "assistant",
      "text": "The operator interface, clean-checkout validation, and production deployment review.",
      "text_sha256": "17b176ddebbcb9f8bd9494ef7580510dd2009f105a70c99a7bff19c94acc7333"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0104",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0104",
      "ordinal": 104,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "The interface should let me choose the fixture, run recovery, inspect claims, and open the exact source note.",
      "text_sha256": "46c9973c4cefad763f791ad72a5d9407d1e06195485b0c70598717b51e0284fe"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0106",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0106",
      "ordinal": 106,
      "role": "user",
      "text": "Do not add editing or cloud controls.",
      "text_sha256": "f0c30188d201f13e5141b8981de5a1814b0207406b32ff37c079d5853fae272b"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0103",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0103",
      "ordinal": 103,
      "role": "assistant",
      "text": "Build the operator interface against the accepted fixture baseline, then test from a clean checkout.",
      "text_sha256": "d334b7f718fd85c6d7e28e00ede109f02158f94008ff00c74501713739524f8c"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "SRC-ATLAS-TURN-0110",
      "conversation_id": "PF-DEMO-ATLAS-WORKSHOP-001",
      "turn_id": "ATLAS-TURN-0110",
